input_str: One of the most anticipated new series this midseason (or 'three week event' rather) is Frank Darabont's Mob City. And to promote TNT's new 1940s set gangster drama, the network has commissioned this poster from legendary artist Drew Struzan...Not to insult the talented artists who crafted the previous posters but Struzan's portrait, shared by the Mob City twitter account, sort of puts them to shame.
